            ">Hundreds <a href="https://apnews.com/article/chad-protest-france-military-agreement-0436a6c9a914c0dd007d603e279e44c8" target=="_blank">protested</a> in Chad on Friday, <strong>calling for the withdrawal of French troops</strong> following the country’s decision to end a defense cooperation agreement with France. Last week, Chad released a statement calling for the <strong>termination of the agreement</strong> but didn’t specify when they had to leave.</p>
