              margin-bottom: 15px;
            "><strong>The most expensive dinosaur fossil ever discovered</strong>, a nearly complete stegosaurus named “Apex,” will be on display at the American Museum of Natural History in New York starting this weekend (<a href="https://apnews.com/article/stegosaurus-apex-skeleton-ken-griffin-nyc-40bfa41cd8e05b7aba54bab27ac69b34" target=="_blank">read more</a>).</p>
            <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              border-left: 3px solid #4c305f;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
